content.rendered:
Corporate Boxing Event: Bouts at Lilydale Youth Centre

Join us for an exciting evening of corporate boxing at the Lilydale Youth Centre, where novice and amateur fighters will showcase their skills and determination in the ring. This event is perfect for both seasoned boxing enthusiasts and those new to the sport, offering thrilling matches that highlight the dedication and spirit of our participants. Experience the thrill of live boxing and support local talent in a family-friendly environment. Don’t miss out on this action-packed event!
